Attribution and design lineage
------------------------------------------------------------------------------
FORGE is an independent VSCode extension whose architecture is informed by the
open-source Cline project (https://github.com/cline/cline, Apache-2.0) — in
particular the OpenAI-compatible provider model and an agentic harness — and by
the open "Agent Skills" standard (SKILL.md with progressive disclosure,
including the `.claude/skills/` layout).

No "Cline" trademark, name, or branding is used in this product. The FORGE name,
flame icon, and branding are project-specific.

